title: Psalm ch83, v18.themepack
description:
This app is not affiliated or endorsed by JW.ORG or any other legal entity. It is designed for personal use.

This theme has the monthly calendar for August 2012 downloaded from Jw.org. I adjusted the calendar however so it only has the month of August, and it is beside it, not under it as it appears in the pdf version downloaded from the site.

If you want the FULL CALENDAR --- Please download your preferable type FOR FREE from 

www.jw.org

Just a simple Theme to Spread The News about the website in August, a historical month. Keep sharing brothers and sisters.

Thank you
